# Agent Layer Architecture

**Before writing any code here, read all of the following:**

- `docs/architecture/agents.md` — agent/skill architecture, state boundaries, factory conventions
- `docs/architecture/integrations.md` — port/adapter pattern and rules
- `docs/architecture/quality-and-delivery.md` — fakes-before-merge requirement, test tagging
- `docs/architecture/persistence.md` — checkpointing and state store API
- `docs/architecture/observability.md` — LangSmith tag schema (`case_id`, `workflow_id`, `step_id`)
